Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}現在的你 全力支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:29.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨無助 我們也要結伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.77,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與朋友們嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}這樣一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依然感到內心的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受盡冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:54.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身於時代的狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:03.50,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇氣與不安 如影相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:11.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 現在就要用我的雙手創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些讓我們受傷感到絕望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我們哭泣感到難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然縈繞於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終將跨過重重障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:32.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:29.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.77,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:54.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:03.50,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:11.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:32.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:46.47,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在哪裏呢？{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.30,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的寶藏{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:56.35,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在即將展開大冒險{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.01,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的陽光{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.03,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶給我啟程的預感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:06.28,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 天空和花朵都在向我微笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.02,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前方等待我的將是什麼呢？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.12,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:18.92,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕開啟夢想之門…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.29,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  走吧！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.63,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂風吹襲{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.30,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使內心動搖{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.01,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使手中握著的是空白的地圖{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.80,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂風吹襲{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.68,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要描繪美好的明天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:38.31,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著遠方  去往何方？ 直到那最終的彼方{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.27,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不言敗{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.06,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不哭泣{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:46.82,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到夢想成真的那一天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.93,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空在微笑{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.57,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花兒也在微笑{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我也一定會開懷大笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:58.96,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何艱難險阻都能跨越{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:04.25,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也 再也…不會害怕了{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:46.47,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにあるのかな{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.30,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクだけの宝物{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:56.35,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 大きな冒険へ{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.01,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな日差し{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.03,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅立ちの予感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:06.28,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空も花も ホラ 笑っている{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.02,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先には何が待つのだろう？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.12,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:18.92,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢の扉にそっと手をかけて…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.29,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  行こう！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.63,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.30,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心揺らしながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.01,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真っ白な地図を片手に持ちながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.80,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.68,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日を描きながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:38.31,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くまで 何処まで？ たどり着けるまで{\fad(200,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.27,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対負けないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.06,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対泣かないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:46.82,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この夢を叶えるその日までは{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.93,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空は笑っていた{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.57,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの花は笑っていた{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクもいつか笑うから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:58.96,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな壁も越えるから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:04.25,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう 何も 何も…コワクナイ{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【註釋】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到在瀨戶海的因島上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:02.29,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因島：瀨戶內海諸島之一 位於廣島東南部\n是本因坊秀策的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17·四 右上角 「小目」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:32.74,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小目」：四個星位周圍靠近角的兩個位置就是小目 棋盤中共有8個小目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尖」?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.93,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尖」：圍棋中在己方原有棋子的斜上或斜下一路處行棋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他用的是很古老的定式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:16:01.76,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「定式」：圍棋活動中長久以來逐漸形成的各種進攻或防守的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這既不是最好的一手 也不是最強的一手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\3c&H000000&}{\pos(425,365)}永遠的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑快點 小明 馬上就到爺爺家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說嘛 直接回家不就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎麼都是些沒用的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 我們走吧 這裏好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自這麼做真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為上次的社會課考試我只考了8分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以零用錢都被扣掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 這個好像不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道 是下五子棋的棋盤對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爺爺以前用過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許可以賣個好價錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事 爺爺一定是忘掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把上面的灰塵擦掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個污跡怎麼也擦不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什麼污跡啊 很乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊 哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我剛剛不是說在這裏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以聽到我的聲音嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以聽到我的聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實沒有什麼污跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 小光 不要說嚇人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爺爺嗎? 快出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所不能的神明啊  萬分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在又再度回到這個世界上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 小光 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 小光出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 你是什麼人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是平安時代在皇宮內教天皇下圍棋的棋師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天 每天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盤 一盤 能夠一直下棋 我感到很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 除了我以外  還有個棋師在教天皇下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 他向天皇進言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說棋師一個就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下讓我們通過對局一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝的一方纔能繼續留下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他決鬥了?誰贏了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋盤上的戰鬥進行得難分難解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正當大家都凝神於棋局上的時侯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我在無意間發現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的棋盒裏竟然混有一個白棋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把那個白子放在自己的勝子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作弊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想說出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是不是把\n我的黑子放進了你自己的勝子裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的伎倆嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是什麼無聊的藉口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁大家注意棋局的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事先混在\n棋盒裏的黑子放到你的勝子裏 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是那樣做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丟臉了 都給朕安靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種下流的手段會在朕的面前發生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕連想都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我無法抑制心中的憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著作弊的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被趕出了皇宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法再生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天之後 我投水自盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還想…還想再下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}我的靈魂無法安息 便附在了那個棋盤上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了很長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了一個少年的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫 虎次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你可以看到我怨恨的淚水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我留在你的心裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎次郎改名為秀策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20歲就成為師傅的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並最終成為14世本因坊秀策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本因坊秀策?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他卻被一種流行病打垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一晚 年僅34歲的他就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋盤上的血跡就是他留下的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 你就附在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了想繼續下棋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我還沒有領悟到「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 聽說你昨天被救護車拉走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你真的沒事嗎? 昨天怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我自己也記不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來的時候已經今天早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家往後傳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是歷史題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來 繼續考試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的事原來不是做夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字叫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的那麼喜歡下棋?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想繼續下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對下棋可是一點興趣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了什麼? 混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做 什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤 沒事吧? 要不要去保健室?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是我不能下棋的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滲入到了你的意識裏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了你那執著了千年的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我有我自己的人生目標哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我以外就不能找別人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:09:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾下下也沒什麼問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的心還是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…到底是誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完的同學再檢查一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 你知道嗎? 天保變革
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天保? 是水野大人發起的那次變革嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好懷念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經和他在屋內對弈過一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那佩裏你認識嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩裏 就是乘坐鋼鐵戰艦來的那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佩裏提督嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那個佩裏提督是在哪兒登陸的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦賀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時還引起很大的轟動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦賀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤 你在自言自語些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考題做完了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一會兒就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過人家身體的時候也不道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 這個時代的女性真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不要在我腦袋裏面吵了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考完試以後就帶你去下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為東京是大城市嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 還有 我們要去哪裏下棋呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋會場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺有時候也會去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是很多喜歡下棋的老伯聚集的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼時代 總有人喜歡下棋的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6}{\pos(295,298)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs15\3c&HDA644B&\be1}平日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6}{\pos(265,342)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs15\3c&HDA644B&\be1}週六日 節假日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz1}{\pos(340,111)\fs20\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\3c&H400000&}skyblue travel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz1}{\pos(340,141)}{\fs16\bord0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1}{\c&H404000&}各種旅遊 租賃業務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-1\pos(413,210)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs24\bord2\b1\3c&HEC2F6F&}紫水圍棋沙龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 都是些老頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是來這裏 什麼都是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰下都可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在這裏寫下你的名字 棋力是多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋力?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒和人對弈過 我想我應該很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有小孩嗎? 我可以和他下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以 但是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找對弈的對手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 我和你下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到裏面下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小孩子要交500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要交錢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他第一次來這兒 就免費招待他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小亮這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塔矢亮 你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進藤光 小學6年級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是6年級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對手是老頭就沒有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的棋力怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但應該很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚卻又很厲害?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先讓你4到5子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓子? 你要讓我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦 我們年齡差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟塔矢亮下還不用讓子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不知天高地厚的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你先下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能下得很慢 請多多見諒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 你真的那麼高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔了140年這麼久…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17·…1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他拿子的姿勢完全像個新手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·十七 右下角 「小目」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·十七 這裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3·十六
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3·十六
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然拿棋的方式像是初學者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是下的棋路卻很穩健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如他自己說的 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 快點下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為什麼他常常會在奇怪的地方停下來?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·十一 這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他毫不理會我的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 與其說是不理會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是輕鬆化解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個白子是你的了 拿下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19·十五
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拿走了可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18·十四
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可以拿下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那9個白子已經被逼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些白子都會成為你的勝子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很輕鬆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 對方也不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些子不是我要拿的 是他不要的棄子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我左上角的9子被逼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還可以控制住中央部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4·十三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8·五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 8·五  是這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這既不是最好的一手 也不是最強的一手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在試探我接下去該怎麼走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在觀察我的棋力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很高的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下完了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然對弈對我來說還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了那麼長的時間 好累哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有個兒童圍棋比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要和小亮對弈再過50年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了!? 怎麼可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮輸了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮的實力可是接近職業水平的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓子了吧? 讓了几子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是執黑先行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了幾目?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果算上5目半貼目的話應該是小亮贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2目之差嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是一個等級
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮輸了是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那孩子說他從沒和別人下過棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從…沒和…別人…下過棋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不習慣的事做起來果然很累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你滿足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 回家寫社會課的作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跑著回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
